  "texts": [
    "Additionally, within the exercise groups, there were differences between the HIIT and MICT groups.",
    "These differences were evident in the \"physical functioning\" indicator after the intervention (p = 0.002), at 6 months (p = 0.023), and at 12 months of follow-up (p = 0.003).",
    "In the \"role-physical\" indicator, differences were observed after the intervention (p = 0.025) and at 12 months of follow-up (p = 0.017).",
    "Furthermore, distinctions were noted in the \"role-emotional\" indicator at the 12-month follow-up (p = 0.014).",
    "In the \"social functioning\" indicator disparities were evident at 6 months (p = 0.010) and at 12 months of follow-up (p = 0.004)."
